Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:54.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.34,0:20:55.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pika!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.01,0:20:59.90,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko piko piko piko piko piko piko piko...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:12.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže co bylo to pero?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.94,0:21:14.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kdoví?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.08,0:21:17.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sestřičko, potkala jsem maminku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.34,0:21:20.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Já vim. Dívala jsem se.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.29,0:21:23.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemohla jsem jít za ní,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:27.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,ale poděkovala jsem jí, jak mi řikal Jukito.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.91,0:21:29.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Vděčim mu za všecko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.81,0:21:31.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ne, v tom se pleteš.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.78,0:21:34.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bylo to tvoje kouzlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.57,0:21:57.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pusť ho do nebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.34,0:21:59.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobře.
